Package com.vmware.appliance.recovery

The com.vmware.appliance.recovery package provides interfaces for backin up and restoring vCenter Appliance configuration.

Package com.vmware.appliance.recovery Description

The com.vmware.appliance.recovery package provides interfaces for backin up and restoring vCenter Appliance configuration. The package is available starting in vSphere 6.7.
